        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - These verses should be read continuously: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "For I lift up my hand to heaven, and say, As I live forever, if I whet my glittering sword, and if my hand take hold on judgment; I will render vengeance to mine enemies,",
        "children": []
